harnessRequest.name: Holistic App Client CellModel Test
harnessRequest.description: Instantiate HolisticAppClient CellModel through the CellModel test harness.

constructorRequest.name: Holistic App Client Kernel
constructorRequest.description: Holistic app client kernel process manages the overall lifecycle of a derived HTML5 client application defined as a directed graph of active cell processes executing within a CellProcessor instance in the browser tab.

JatYSE8JQj6GxT8AOsbssQ.name: Holistic App Client Kernel
JatYSE8JQj6GxT8AOsbssQ.description: Holistic app client kernel process manages the overall lifecycle of a derived HTML5 client application defined as a directed graph of active cell processes executing within a CellProcessor instance in the browser tab.

PPL45jw5RDWSMNsB97WIWg.name: Holistic Client App Kernel
PPL45jw5RDWSMNsB97WIWg.description: This model manages, tracks, and controls the lifecycle of the client application.

ZE1JY82CQ5uRlWQ-zgqz5g.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Cell Plane Error Handler
ZE1JY82CQ5uRlWQ-zgqz5g.description: This action is dispatched generically by a CellProcessor's intrinsic Cell Process Manager process when it receives a notification from its contained OPC instance of a cell plane error(s) that occurred during the processing of the last external call to CellProcessor.act method.

JwE4LMvpRGC3Jsg1RDjJ1Q.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Hook DOM Events
JwE4LMvpRGC3Jsg1RDjJ1Q.description: Registers DOM event handlers on behalf of the Holistic App Client Kernel process needed to track application lifespan and provide core services.

h-auSE-OSP2TG1jh_3EQ1Q.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Receive DOM Event
h-auSE-OSP2TG1jh_3EQ1Q.description: ControllerAction that signals the Holistic App Client Kernel process of the occurance of a previously-hooked DOM event.

mmLcuWywTe6lUL9OtMJisg.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Signal Lifecycle Event
mmLcuWywTe6lUL9OtMJisg.description: Forwards a holistic app client lifecycle signal to the derived client application's daemon proces.

qzMWhMstQ4Ki06O75y5hMA.name: DOM Location Processor
qzMWhMstQ4Ki06O75y5hMA.description: Abstracts monitoring and setting the window.location and hashroute.

-1Ptaq_zTUa8Gfv_3ODtDg.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: DOM Location Processor
-1Ptaq_zTUa8Gfv_3ODtDg.description: Hooks and monitors DOM location events and publishes them via an observable frame latch. Also, provids programmatic control over DOM location.

TlGPCf7uSf2cZMGZCcU85A.name: DOM Client Location Proccessor: Initialize
TlGPCf7uSf2cZMGZCcU85A.description: Adds a listener to the brower's 'hashchange' event and redirects subsequent event callbacks to the ControllerAction peTmTek_SB64-ofd_PSGj.

peTmTek_SB64-ofd_PSGjg.name: DOM Client Location Processor: 'hashchange'
peTmTek_SB64-ofd_PSGjg.description: Accepts info about the 'hashchange' event and encapsulates the details of updating the DOM Client Locaiton Processor APM memory to record the event details.

RyMcv3MpTI-Co1EyVOIvlw.name: Holarchy CML
RyMcv3MpTI-Co1EyVOIvlw.description: Holarchy Cell Model Library (CML) provides cellular process primitive operations, actions, and cell models for re-use in higher-order cell models.

c2cq2OE9SiaLKahL3Mk0KA.name: Holarchy Base Cell Model
c2cq2OE9SiaLKahL3Mk0KA.description: A collection of low-level building blocks.

U5iIpgd8SHCk7pvaciVLTQ.name: Holarchy Base Memory Mailbox Flag
U5iIpgd8SHCk7pvaciVLTQ.description: A primitive cell process that signals (via process step transition) when some actor has put a message in the mailbox namespace.

z_mTe02hSWmaM1iRO1pBeA.name: Abstract Frame Latch
z_mTe02hSWmaM1iRO1pBeA.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

iyvk_9vhRn2qvrjOes5v7Q.name: Frame Latch: Write
iyvk_9vhRn2qvrjOes5v7Q.description: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.

MDVBKW89TvO9T62Ge7GmNg.name: Holarchy Core Actions & Operators
MDVBKW89TvO9T62Ge7GmNg.description: Low-level glue models, actions, and operators for building re-usable infrastructure for execution within an ObservableProcessController (OPC) runtime host instance.

RW8Y2O-kRNSv87yXT962wQ.name: Holarchy Core Logic Actions & Operators
RW8Y2O-kRNSv87yXT962wQ.description: A collection of TranitionOperator plug-ins that implement generic logic functions AND, OR, NOT, TRUE.

YgABX95wR86GCYrYaDLISA.name: Logical AND
YgABX95wR86GCYrYaDLISA.description: Returns Boolean true iff all suboperations return true.

0JIva4IFSm6Xm7i38g8uUA.name: Logical OR
0JIva4IFSm6Xm7i38g8uUA.description: Returns Boolean true iff any suboperations return true.

TLSHkl73SO-utuzM7dyN2g.name: Logical NOT
TLSHkl73SO-utuzM7dyN2g.description: Returns Boolean true iff the suboperator returns false (i.e. it logically complements or inverts whatever operator it's applied to).

e89cwnP4Qd6MocAhzdOJgw.name: Logical TRUE
e89cwnP4Qd6MocAhzdOJgw.description: Always returns Boolean true. Used typically to unilaterally transition a cell process from one step to another (e.g. always, or as a default after many other transition rules).

jQxlhOe-RDilxY0sNIierQ.name: Holarchy Core Memory Actions & Operators
jQxlhOe-RDilxY0sNIierQ.description: A collection of ControllerAction & TransitionOperator plug-ins that perform logical comparisons operatations on cell processs memory.

oaF3-dXwQkusjD3I2o9-8g.name: OCD Array Length Equal to Value
oaF3-dXwQkusjD3I2o9-8g.description: Returns Boolean true iff the length of the array stored at OCD path equals the specified numerical value (direct or indirect).

2w7n6KxdR8mdIliePJesLQ.name: OCD Namespace A ? B Value Comparison
2w7n6KxdR8mdIliePJesLQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff operand A and B values compare using the indicated comparison operator. Note either A and/or B may be specified by value or path.

UeLs9PcASwuC7KR190eYhA.name: OCD Boolean Flag Is Set
UeLs9PcASwuC7KR190eYhA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated Boolean flag namespace is true.

ggsavKiARsq7rjwn-lxdfA.name: OCD Namespace Is Greater Than Value
ggsavKiARsq7rjwn-lxdfA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is greater than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

k7THIKKDQMKOac1Rxh9tEQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Identical To Value
k7THIKKDQMKOac1Rxh9tEQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is identical (i.e. strictly equal (===)) to the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

XxX_a1sQS1OlJbWAYfx6tQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Less Than Value
XxX_a1sQS1OlJbWAYfx6tQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is less than the indicated value. Limited to number and string value comparisons only.

kD1PcgqYQlm7fJatNG2ZsA.name: OCD Namespace Is Truthy
kD1PcgqYQlm7fJatNG2ZsA.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is truthy.

pj9a6tQpSXWp7WZZ8VbKLQ.name: OCD Namespace Is Array Empty
pj9a6tQpSXWp7WZZ8VbKLQ.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace value is an array AND value.length !== 0.

fS5liuD1RBSdaPBEhsoxXw.name: OCD Namespace Is Map Keyless
fS5liuD1RBSdaPBEhsoxXw.description: Returns Boolean true iff the indicated OCD namespace is declared as a map in the OCD filter spec AND the OCD value is an object AND Object.key(value) !== 0.

Ve_kEFkGSMSgOqUWu9Yo_w.name: OCD Read Namespace Indirect
Ve_kEFkGSMSgOqUWu9Yo_w.description: Reads and returns the value of OCD namespace via path indirection.

5rFEDGLYRSiZCeChMnkCHQ.name: OCD Boolean Flag Set
5rFEDGLYRSiZCeChMnkCHQ.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value true.

_yxWfFLnTqqN-UxRdd7W5w.name: OCD Boolean Flag Clear
_yxWfFLnTqqN-UxRdd7W5w.description: Set the Boolean-type OCD namespace specified by path to value false.

YtwGXxryRyaNnxwc9NGJiQ.name: Holarchy Core Utility Actions & Operators
YtwGXxryRyaNnxwc9NGJiQ.description: A collection of ControllerAction & TransitionOperator plug-ins that are of general use when building custom APM's in particular.

aXju3wSBQnufe0r51Y04wg.name: Holarchy Core Util: Action Response Writer
aXju3wSBQnufe0r51Y04wg.description: A low-level utility action that dispatches a subaction returning the response to the caller and writing it also to the indicated OCD response namespace.

UX7JquBhSZO0QyEk7u9-sw.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor
UX7JquBhSZO0QyEk7u9-sw.description: Manages the DOM display via @encapsule/d2r2 and React.

IxoJ83u0TXmG7PLUYBvsyg.name: Holistic Client App Kernel: d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor
IxoJ83u0TXmG7PLUYBvsyg.description: Manages the details of initializing and dynamically updating the client application view (DOM display surface) via @encapsule/d2r2 and Facebook React.

ENIOOasYSdmJj_RXjA__hQ.name: d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor: Rydrate/Render
ENIOOasYSdmJj_RXjA__hQ.description: Rehydrate and/or render/re-render client application view via d2r2/React transport using context and render data obtained from specified input paths in the OCD.

vrmv3WMRQXql7Bx3DDEIDw.name: Holistic Client App View Manager
vrmv3WMRQXql7Bx3DDEIDw.description: Provides management of client view cells in a holistic client app.

Hsu-43zBRgqHItCPWPiBng.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Client View Processor
Hsu-43zBRgqHItCPWPiBng.description: Encapsulates the high-level details of selecting, creating, and updating d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor update signals.

74npOB-3S8GEgHwdtWwHrg.name: Holistic App Common Kernel
74npOB-3S8GEgHwdtWwHrg.description: Provides core kernel cell process models shared by the holistic app server and holistic app client application cell models.

ABn1MUgSQT2dy8Lri8xDbA.name: View Theme Processor
ABn1MUgSQT2dy8Lri8xDbA.description: The ViewThemeProcessor cell model provides a simple service for generating a Holistic App Theme JSON document used to dynamically style display elements via React.

zzvzLbm2RTyQN1lWFcjpVA.name: Theme Processor Model
zzvzLbm2RTyQN1lWFcjpVA.description: Encapsulates the details of generating and updating current programmatic style settings consumed by client application view and display processes.

e2kGs2nLRwW7RtFDPi8REg.name: Read Theme Palette
e2kGs2nLRwW7RtFDPi8REg.description: Reads (and updates if necessary) the current theme output.

UK08qja3QiaHFGhl99fbmg.name: ViewThemeProcessor::Write Settings
UK08qja3QiaHFGhl99fbmg.description: Update the whole or part of the ViewThemeProcessor model's input theme settings document.

apm.name: Abstract Frame Latch
apm.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

apm.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: Client View Processor
apm.description: Encapsulates the high-level details of selecting, creating, and updating d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor update signals.

apm.name: Holistic App Client Kernel: DOM Location Processor
apm.description: Hooks and monitors DOM location events and publishes them via an observable frame latch. Also, provids programmatic control over DOM location.

apm.name: Holistic Client App Kernel
apm.description: This model manages, tracks, and controls the lifecycle of the client application.

apm.name: Holistic Client App Kernel: d2r2/React Client Display Adaptor
apm.description: Manages the details of initializing and dynamically updating the client application view (DOM display surface) via @encapsule/d2r2 and Facebook React.

apm.name: Theme Processor Model
apm.description: Encapsulates the details of generating and updating current programmatic style settings consumed by client application view and display processes.
